{"tid":130990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[開估]NASA於40ly外TRAPPIST-1發現7宜居類地系外行星目前最多","createTime":"2017-02-22T18:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T04:35:03.000Z","uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e47ba64bd24b0e4ce1f7daf9e6e95bde6251c26","tid":130990,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-telescope-reveals-largest-batch-of-earth-size-habitable-zone-planets-around\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fpress-release%2Fnasa-telescope-reveals-largest-batch-of-earth-size-habitable-zone-planets-around&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f57d0ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nasa.gov/press-release/nasa-telescope-reveals-largest-batch-of-earth-size-habitable-zone-planets-around</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://exoplanets.nasa.gov/trappist1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexoplanets.nasa.gov%2Ftrappist1%2F&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a75e6eb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://exoplanets.nasa.gov/trappist1/</a>"},{"pid":"0d2ec6c64dc11e8441558f56005581d58723be48","tid":130990,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nasa.gov/sites/default/files/styles/full_width/public/thumbnails/image/1_main_pia21423-png.png?itok=2Stv_aWu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasa.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Ffull_width%2Fpublic%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F1_main_pia21423-png.png%3Fitok%3D2Stv_aWu&h=e6cac235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bnKFaAS30X8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbnKFaAS30X8&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUyi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=615a79a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bnKFaAS30X8</a> <br />\n<img src=\"https://